The opening activity is the Login where the user is asked for his credentials and the information is checked if it is true.
Then the app moves to Options where there are options for:
1) GETQuery: get a patient and its details
2) PostQuery: post a patient and its details
3) Create_Activity: create a sensor and also mention the concepts to be mapped
4) Sensorconcept: First retrieve the sensor concepts and take respective readings for them and post.
5) GetIput: take input from another app